targets.expression:
fields CbsSensorId as CbsId
| filter strcontains("$CBS_ID", CbsId)
| stats count() by CbsId, Workload
| sort by Workload

filter level = 'INFO'
|filter strcontains("$CBS_ID", CbsId)
| stats count() by CbsId, Workload
| sort by Workload
